{"tid":2261352,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"聽障生涉搶胡椒噴霧被控襲警 辯方指遭警暴迫招認","createTime":"2020-10-28T08:46:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-28T11:46:26.000Z","uid":56115,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1d0328ee6e192f4600195c6c6cbe789da846b86d","tid":2261352,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T08:46:46.000Z","msg":"辯方今陳詞指，被告當日遭約10名警員包圍，有警員以警棍大力擊打被告的背脊、後腳、肋骨及後腦，及後有警員壓著被告，扯脫其助聽器和口罩，並朝他臉上噴胡椒噴劑。其間被告雖然不斷重申自己有聽障，但遭警員斥罵：「收聲啦你！」<br />\n<br />\n當被告被帶到警署後，曾要求致電母親，卻遭負責警員拒絕。負責警員更在被告未有母親陪同下補錄口供。及後母親到場，警員向兩人謂「男子漢大丈夫，做錯就要認」，並指被告若願意認罪，法官會給予三分一刑期減免，並可判感化，結果被告與母親均在口供紙上簽名。"},{"pid":"87e5d05e6c3c6e7cde65d3f5a5d6ee560356609b","tid":2261352,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T08:47:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201028/VZGNXAHCKNHVHOUTYMQXFA4N4M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201028%2FVZGNXAHCKNHVHOUTYMQXFA4N4M%2F&d=wqADD7%2BrbugmZDmBsEVo7IGitI067obQ02bu1xQE4oc%3D&h=b0806ac9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201028%2FVZGNXAHCKNHVHOUTYMQXFA4N4M%2F&h=345120f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201028/VZGNXAHCKNHVHOUTYMQXFA4N4M/</a>"},{"pid":"adb69376c102537186b84ca424ea301b9980f3b7","tid":2261352,"uid":51271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T08:53:07.000Z","msg":"屈打成招"},{"pid":"b9d1113c9e104c1f35ddb5b9568350caedc33bc8","tid":2261352,"uid":8014,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T08:55:04.000Z","msg":"做黃絲一日要好嬲好嬲幾多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11e79509a83efedbf1053af46344abeba3982669","tid":2261352,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T09:03:05.000Z","msg"