","msg":"辯方律師追問警員對此事不知情的原因，卻隨即遭裁判官<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">鄭紀航</span></span>打斷「啱啱佢咪講咗囉，點解要再問？」辯方未有繼續追問。<br />\n<br />\n辯方指，實際上被告接受警誡時未有戴上助聽器，警誡後亦沒有任何回應，而「一時衝動」這句是被告要求沖洗臉部時說出，而非警誡之下說。警員不同意。<br />\n<br />\n依單又係鄭紀航"},{"pid":"a088a3d11c0124918f6855ca56d8cee2ca319cd9","tid":2261352,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T11:16:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffec5fb783a1e4dbb2c930a1a7be8e4265db0d00","tid":2261352,"uid":5094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T11:24:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eef644486b343b15393ecf5f2f6705da4e168e58","tid":2261352,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T11:40:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/20201028-1920copy_Y3b0Q_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F20201028-1920copy_Y3b0Q_1200x0.png&h=23b8c18b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E8%81%BD%E9%9A%9C%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E6%90%B6%E8%83%A1%E6%A4%92%E5%99%B4%E9%9C%A7%E4%BD%BF%E8%AD%A6%E5%8F%B8%E8%B7%8C%E5%80%92-%E8%AD%A6%E5%8F%B8-%E9%9B%99%E8%86%9D-%E7%88%9B%E5%92%97-%E5%8F%B3%E8%86%9D%E6%BB%B2%E8%A1%80/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E8%2581%25BD%25E9%259A%259C%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%2590%25B6%25E8%2583%25A1%25E6%25A4%2592%25E5%2599%25B4%25E9%259C%25A7%25E4%25BD%25BF%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%258F%25B8%25E